---
layout: base.njk
pageTitle: Just Piano Things
description: Piano tips, guides, and insights from Jake Wells — your Kansas City piano tuner. Learn about tuning, buying pianos, and keeping your instrument in top shape.
permalink: /justpianothings/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <h1>Just Piano Things</h1>
  <p class="page-subtitle">Tips, guides, and insights from your local piano tuner</p>
</section>

<section class="blog-listing">
  {% for post in collections.blog %}
  <article class="blog-card">
    <a href="{{ post.url }}">
      <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
      <div class="blog-card-meta">
        <time>{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <span class="blog-card-author">{{ post.data.author or site.owner }}</span>
      </div>
      {% if post.data.excerpt %}
      <p class="blog-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </a>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
